In [307]:
def visualzie_KPI(start=0, end=16, i_16=None, single_index=None):
    if i_16 is not None:
        start = i_16 * 16
        end = (i_16+1) * 16
    
    if single_index is not None:
        start = single_index
        end = single_index + 1
        
    kpi_names = pf_df['name'].unique()
    i=0
    print("index", start, "to", end)
    for kpi in kpi_names[start: end]:
        i+=1
        pf_1 = pf_df[pf_df.name == kpi]
        if end-start>1:
            ax=plt.subplot(4,4,i)
            legend = False
        else:
            ax=plt.subplot(1,1,i)
            legend = True
            plt.title(kpi)
        sns.lineplot(x="ts", y="value", hue="cmdb_id", data=pf_1, ax=ax, legend=legend, alpha=0.5)

def plot_trace(index = 0):

    trace_1 = trace_df[(trace_df.type == t) & (trace_df.service == s)]
    sns.lineplot(x="ts", y="time", hue="cmdb", data=trace_1, legend=True, alpha=0.5)
